{"tid":2186164,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"THE世界大學排名公布　理大急升42位","createTime":"2020-09-02T17:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T03:25:30.000Z","uid":225931,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b85da43d7b13b05546d83b5f7d05cef5aa73d969","tid":2186164,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T17:52:13.000Z","msg":"《泰晤士高等教育》（Times Higher Education，THE）今日（2日）公布2021年世界大學排名。本港有5間大學躋身首200位，當中香港大學排名下跌4位至全球第39位，去年經歷反修例激烈衝突的理工大學則躍升42位至全球第129位。<br />\n<br />\n英國牛津大學今年連續第五年蟬聯全球首位；亞洲地區中，清華大學排名全球20位，成為亞洲排名最高的學府。本港大學方面，中大比去年上升一位，科大跌9位，兩校並列全球第56位；城大排名維持不變，列全球第126位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5e6ba4578e11c2b93e7bfcd46a7cf9aefcd7d9","tid":2186164,"uid":367769,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T17:54:29.000Z","msg":"升咗咁多都仲係低過shitty<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b69222edde22e57da9abd6c79737c1022c88af5","tid":2186164,"uid":79562,"like":14,"dislike":8,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T17:57:41.000Z","msg":"都係個句 東大點會唔係亞洲第一<br />\n語言排名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae811477d62192ca432b489fd93c51b8ebe5dd4","tid":2186164,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T17:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac1cc6c64bff5157b25da126c500f479a025d6b","tid":2186164,"uid":37197,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"8d5e6ba4578e11c2b93e7bfcd46a7cf9aefcd7d9","tid":2186164,"uid":367769,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T17:54:29.000Z","msg":"升咗咁多都仲係低過shitty<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr